{"tid":1634361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【賽後檢討】依條片話你知點解琴日前線俾人捉咗廿幾個！","createTime":"2019-10-07T07:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T13:30:07.000Z","uid":34780,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"ae35872ddcf5fbff5b4b0cd242cf1cc1a27be654","tid":1634361,"uid":34780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:37:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YcIur1IiVj0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYcIur1IiVj0&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=14b4c032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YcIur1IiVj0</a><br />\n<br />\n睇片所知<br />\n1.本身前線同狗有一段距離<br />\n2.其實中後排本身已經企得夠疏<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p3T6SmE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp3T6SmE.jpg&h=64b2f161&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問題在於<br />\n雖然企得夠疏 但中後排接收唔到有狗衝緊嘅訊息<br />\n導致中後排仲以為係1212慢慢撤<br />\n塞死咗前線走唔到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XaJFWOA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXaJFWOA.jpg&h=c9f47d01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mUZegOz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmUZegOz.jpg&h=82731958&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建議解決方法<br />\n用不同哨子聲區分俾中後排知幾時係慢慢退幾時要全力跑 (但依個方法係放緊tg嗰陣用唔到)<br />\n<br />\n歡迎各巴絲獻計解決依個損兵折將嘅缺口"},{"pid":"6e8d907a1e6f01a04b1dc8af37ac7bf5ea266ee3","tid":1634361,"uid":5763,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:39:59.000Z","msg":"人數好多,如果全部和里非唔驚,夠膽救得返最前面D手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c81eae68113bfe8233429040ce558af1d102d54","tid":1634361,"uid":106929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:43:42.000Z","msg":"塞死晒... 見到有D前線 混入左人群走左 <br />\n好多都係 前邊幾排 食花生比人拉晒"},{"pid":"d5d508187536e1003e81d6ded06ec9e35f5e4a1d","tid":1634361,"uid":201605,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:45:21.000Z","msg":"依家啲狗係狗沖埋黎<br />\n人數唔夠狗黎打，就唔好再1212啦<br />\n亦都唔排除現場有25狗叫人唔好跑"},{"pid":"5e5e1bf3d018b762c5851af106f0fb39cc727617","tid":1634361,"uid":34780,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6e8d907a1e6f01a04b1dc8af37ac7bf5ea266ee3","tid":1634361,"uid":5763,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:39:59.000Z","msg":"人數好多,如果全部和里非唔驚,夠膽救得返最前面D手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:46:52.000Z","msg":"自問自己都唔夠膽救人 <br />\n見到狗係面前追人會腳軟<br />\n好佩服勇武成日救手足<br />\n佢地好大勇氣 <br />\n<br />\n其實如果琴日中排和理非收到準確資訊肯全力跑<br />\n前線手足就唔洗塞死係度俾狗咬<br />\n個12歲𡃁妹仲驚到個人震晒<br />\n睇到好撚心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以一定要檢討反省改善策略"},{"pid":"6379cb458719b05bd8fafc04f615d6ef4da41aad","tid":1634361,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:48:32.000Z","msg":"4個月喇 屌你 每次見到我都把撚火 個個行行企企 個頭隔個街口講左放煙霧 個個冇危機感"},{"pid":"55c47f8629dfe5714679d03f1881d638c1ff0c48","tid":1634361,"uid":76609,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:50:12.000Z","msg":"無論如何，有危機意識，<br />\n任何時時候都唔好慢慢散咪得，<br />\n唔好同我講冇體力，<br />\n一係你就去練，一係就唔好行咁前，<br />\n你行得前又冇體力係累到人，<br />\n唔係你自己一個人嘅事，<br />\n而家打緊仗，你同人講你冇體力人地就唔打你？"},{"pid":"0e4f653081c10394380cc889c3933ed9b8f645bd","tid":1634361,"uid":34780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d5d508187536e1003e81d6ded06ec9e35f5e4a1d","tid":1634361,"uid":201605,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:45:21.000Z","msg":"依家啲狗係狗沖埋黎<br />\n人數唔夠狗黎打，就唔好再1212啦<br />\n亦都唔排除現場有25狗叫人唔好跑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:50:18.000Z","msg":"好多中後排仲1212<br />\n明明啲狗已經衝緊上嚟<br />\n前線驚撚仆街<br />\n中後慢行塞住咗<br />\n見到前線好絕望<br />\n<br />\n一定要揾到方法傳到正確訊息俾中後排先可以解決到個問題"},{"pid":"e132bd903ee11cbe140e652c210971927075a9e2","tid":1634361,"uid":331636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:55:38.000Z","msg":"走到就走<br />\n走唔到,必要時掟開武器,唔好斷正,踢保後又一條好漢<br />\n另外真係可能要係中間加個哨兵"},{"pid":"01518eb8b22f1b5cad4626970be93f4c96ab893c","tid":1634361,"uid":34780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"55c47f8629dfe5714679d03f1881d638c1ff0c48","tid":1634361,"uid":76609,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:50:12.000Z","msg":"無論如何，有危機意識，<br />\n任何時時候都唔好慢慢散咪得，<br />\n唔好同我講冇體力，<br />\n一係你就去練，一係就唔好行咁前，<br />\n你行得前又冇體力係累到人，<br />\n唔係你自己一個人嘅事，<br />\n而家打緊仗，你同人講你冇體力人地就唔打你？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:56:18.000Z","msg":"我覺得唔多唔少都係因為好多時候明明現場咩事都冇發生<br />\n但啲人就突然1212之後就狂跑<br />\n跑多咗變咗狼來了咁<br />\n啲人麻目咗 所以危機意識低咗<br />\n<br />\n今次就證明傳遞準確訊息真係好撚重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905c8386dea2d7e217dc56bd72ad355866d916dd","tid":1634361,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0602b040e70a0a1832bc5045c21b979b02210d24","tid":1634361,"uid":34780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e132bd903ee11cbe140e652c210971927075a9e2","tid":1634361,"uid":331636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:55:38.000Z","msg":"走到就走<br />\n走唔到,必要時掟開武器,唔好斷正,踢保後又一條好漢<br />\n另外真係可能要係中間加個哨兵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:58:07.000Z","msg":"巴打依個建議唔錯 <br />\n係前線哨兵聯絡中排哨兵<br />\n真係大撤退時<br />\n由中排哨兵吹哨子叫和理非快跑"},{"pid":"0ba9288bcf226149746e90525f4332b67f2293ec","tid":1634361,"uid":126868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:58:51.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"c3978995a42ce4d054e838a4c79a2c299466e39c","tid":1634361,"uid":105740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:01:25.000Z","msg":"真心 發夢果陣前中後排都真係需要多啲哨 現場資訊傳得太慢"},{"pid":"ac23a6633fedce1177e53f6ca905678c27a9abc2","tid":1634361,"uid":34780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3978995a42ce