:0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:31:40.000Z","msg":"最理想係打狗救人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:45:14.000Z","msg":"琴日中後排個班唔敢上前打狗，但好多人都叫唔好退太後、退無可退。有準備救人<br />\n<br />\n點知狗一衝中前排退，中後排個班焗住退"},{"pid":"1ffaef93e03a3123c70e28dae179ed1d83b25a08","tid":1634361,"uid":268550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae35872ddcf5fbff5b4b0cd242cf1cc1a27be654","tid":1634361,"uid":34780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:37:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YcIur1IiVj0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYcIur1IiVj0&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=14b4c032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YcIur1IiVj0</a><br />\n<br />\n睇片所知<br />\n1.本身前線同狗有一段距離<br />\n2.其實中後排本身已經企得夠疏<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p3T6SmE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp3T6SmE.jpg&h=64b2f161&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問題在於<br />\n雖然企得夠疏 但中後排接收唔到有狗衝緊嘅訊息<br />\n導致中後排仲以為係1212慢慢撤<br />\n塞死咗前線走唔到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XaJFWOA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXaJFWOA.jpg&h=c9f47d01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mUZegOz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmUZegOz.jpg&h=82731958&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建議解決方法<br />\n用不同哨子聲區分俾中後排知幾時係慢慢退幾時要全力跑 (但依個方法係放緊tg嗰陣用唔到)<br />\n<br />\n歡迎各巴絲獻計解決依個損兵折將嘅缺口"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:51:44.000Z","msg":"點都好主要原因就係中後排啲人走得慢! 慢慢走害死人!  我哋要全體都知道有事要狂走得快！ 這個心理準備最重要！ 乜雞都冇用！ Repeat 鐘後排有事要走得極快如果唔係會害死人㗎!!"},{"pid":"8433be4a61f3aacf94597894e8dcac655fab0ec4","tid":1634361,"uid":34780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6710c08735338c777212a532f4e86e76ce713b76","tid":1634361,"uid":62516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:35:04.000Z","msg":"有同樣睇法<br />\n之前有手足提過用手機燈做signal<br />\n其實有發